{"ts":"2026-06-27T13:25:30.609Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Verifying Filtering Scope**\n\nI'm now confirming the backend's checks, particularly focusing on authorization, as I noticed I need to handle token checks correctly. Specifically, I'm checking `getAuthCaller(req)` from `app/api/v1/dashboard/admin/route.ts` and `/client/route.ts` to ensure robust authorization for both roles.\n\n\n","redacted":false}}
